title: Tech women's golf team wraps up final two rounds at RiverTowne Invitational - Tennessee Tech
content: Tech women's golf team wraps up final two rounds at RiverTowne Invitational  Tennessee Tech
description: MT. PLEASANT, S.C. – The Tennessee Tech women's golf team concluded action at the RiverTowne Invitational Tuesday afternoon, completing the remaining holes left from Monday’s second round as well as the entirety of the third and final round.
